2002-2016 (La. 10/14/02)

Jewell Amy FLATAU and Edison Paul Flatau v. ST. LOUIS PLANTING, INC., et al. No. 2002-CC-2016. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re St. Louis Planting Inc. et al.; Gay, John F.; Gay, Andrew Price; Louisiana Farm Bureau Casualty Ins. Co.; — Defendants); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Iberville, 18th Judicial District Court Div. C, No. 52,717; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2002 CW 0414.

Denied.

KIMBALL, J., would grant the writ. VICTORY, J., would grant the writ. WEIMER, J., would grant the writ.
